### Smart Task - KanbanController API Test
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Auth
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Dynamic IDs
@projectId = REPLACE_PROJECT_ID
@taskId = REPLACE_TASK_ID
@statusId = REPLACE_STATUS_ID

### 1) Get Kanban board by project (columns + tasks)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/kanban
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2) Create new task status (owner/admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/statuses
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "In Review"
}

### 3) Drag & drop task to another status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "statusId": "{{statusId}}"
}
